You kinda messed up naming the episodes. I checked wikipedia, and it says BTR Season 2 Episode 24 is "Big Time Strike", not "Big Time Superheroes".

Not angry or complaining though. Just asking you to  cite the episodes accurately. ^^
Can you upload other shows like Disney shows like wizards and Nickelodeon shows Victorious?

@mikeyblitz21 -- uploader must have taken the show title out of the torrent because it's not there anymore.

But per imdb.com Episode 24 is in fact Big Time Superheros. Wikipedia is not always the most accurate source to get your information from. 

Big Time Strike is S02E22
Big Time Superheroes S02E24
